  "text": "The cholinesterase activities were measured based on Ellman et al. 's method [CITATION_1] . The increase of absorbance was monitored at 412 nm in a reaction mixture containing DMSO for the control group) were preincubated with the enzyme during 10 minutes at room temperature, and the reaction was started with the addition of acetylthiocholine or butyrylthiocholine (0.8 mM).",
